<P>
   AFIA-TV-REVIEW (Undated) _ Walter Goodman reviews Frontline's
``Mafia Power Play,'' Tuesday night at 10 on PBS.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; STYLE (Moved in ``l'' category) &QL; 
 &LR;
</P>
<P>
   FASHION-PARIS (Paris) _ Review from Paris of Celine, Cerruti,
Galliano, Chanel, Lacroix, Loewe, Gaultier, Montana, and Scott. By
Karen Horyn.
