<P>
   &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  Here is a list of  &UR; CAMPAIGN &LR;  stories that moved through 2:30
a.m. today, on The N.Y. Times News Service. &UR;
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  The stories go backward to 6:30 a.m. the previous day.
