<P>
   COXNET WHEELS 1012_ Depending upon viewpoint, the 2000
Mitsubishi Montero Sport Limited's primary characteristic is either
its main strength or weakness. That's because, like its full-size
big brother, the midsize Sport Limited rides on a truck-type
platform. (DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) Art includes
4-column color photo of 2000 Mitsubishi Montero Sport Limited and a
18-pica color photo of the SUV's interior.
