</P>
<P>
   AT A GLANCE _ Fact box previewing the 2000 Mitsubishi Montero
Sport Limited.
</P>
<P>
   SHARP DRIVING _ The auto industry recently experienced a major
passing _ the final Ford Taurus SHO rolled off the assembly line.
Should we all be wearing black? No, because while the car we love
is no longer being made, there are still many thousands of them on
the road. (Sharp, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). Includes 1-column
color photograph of columnist.
</P>
<P>
   TESTDRIVE-CAVALIER _ Russ reviews the Chevrolet Cavalier.
(DeVault, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). MOVED.
