</P>
<P>
   Procter &AMP; Gamble and Yahoo! have united to market P&AMP;G's Pringles
crisps, Pepto-Bismol medicine and Pampers diapers.
</P>
<P>
   They are using banners and e-mails to bring traffic to the site
and sweepstakes to get users to register. &QL; 
