(707) 226-9991. Tasting room open by appointment only.
</P>
<P>
   _  &UR; Greens &LR; , Building A, Fort Mason, San Francisco; (415)
771-6222. Lunch Tuesday-Saturday; dinner Monday-Saturday; brunch
Sunday.
</P>
<P>
   _  &UR; Laura Chenel Chevre &LR; , (707) 996-4477. Not open to the public.
Chevre is available at specialty grocers and many supermarkets.
