Texas Limousine is one of the concerned operators. Some of his
clients hire limousines for proms in Dallas, where he has to keep
an eye out _ so he won't be ticketed. ``I've been told that they've
got two people in Dallas who enforce the regulations, mainly during
prom season. They hang out at the hotels, watching to catch
somebody,'' he says. So far, Goodbread has been lucky. ``I guess I
just haven't been caught.'' The problem that Goodbread has with
