BAPTIST FOUNDATION OF AMERICA PACKAGE &QL; 
 &QL; 
AFFINITY FRAUD (Phoenix) - It's a seductive thought _ give money to
a good cause, and get a good return. Most of the investors in the
Baptist Foundation of America were drawn to it because it was
``doing God's work.'' The sting of mismanagement is even stronger
when the organization that does you in ostensibly shares your
values, ethics or religion. And there are more and more shysters
and incompetents out there ready to prey on those who want their
investors to do good. We will talk to national experts in this
