two years, or more. This story should touch on the key factors in
this developing story: the concept of affinity fraud, the lack of
regulation, the long list of victims, not to mention the Baptist
Church itself. We'll investigate the civil cases already filed,
explain the scope of the state investigation, and what likely will
happen next. By RICCARDO DAVIS and HALL MATTERN. Story will move in
the ``A'' category. &QL; 
