Addicks/Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   (NYT33) ATLANTA -- Oct. 12, 1999 -- BBN-METS-BRAVES-2, 10-12 --
Atlanta Braves pitcher Greg Maddux fires one at New York Mets John
Olerud in the first inning in Game 1 of the National League
Championship Series on Tuesday at Turner Field. (Rich
Addicks/Atlanta Journal-Constitution) LITE
</P>
